<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Relieving and Experience Letter</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: "Calibri", Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 12pt;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #000;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .page {
      position: relative;
      width: 210mm;
      height: 297mm; /* A4 size */
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-image: url('<%= letterheadPath %>');
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      background-size: 100% 100%;
      background-position: center;
    }

    .content {
      position: absolute;
      top: 115mm; /* ⬆️ lowered slightly (was 105mm) for correct vertical alignment */
      left: 30mm;
      right: 25mm;
      bottom: 35mm; /* leaves space for address bar */
    }

    .date {
      text-align: left;
      margin: 0 0 16px 0; /* ⬆️ slightly increased for breathing room under the logo */
    }

    .title {
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-decoration: underline;
      margin: 18px 0 28px 0; /* ⬆️ added more gap below heading */
    }

    .paragraph {
      text-align: justify;
      margin: 0 0 10px 0;
    }

    .sincere-line {
      margin-top: 25px;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }

    .for-company-line {
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .signature {
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .note {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 25mm;
      left: 30mm;
      right: 25mm;
      font-size: 10pt;
      text-align: left;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page">
    <div class="content">
      <p class="date">
        <%= new Date(relieving_date).toLocaleDateString('en-GB').replace(/\//g, '-') %>
      </p>

      <p class="title">Relieving and Experience Letter</p>

      <!-- ✅ Added slightly more gap (15px) below the title -->
      <div style="height: 15px;"></div>

      <p class="paragraph"><strong>Employee Name:</strong> <%= employee_name %></p>
      <% if (employee_id) { %>
        <p class="paragraph"><strong>Employee ID:</strong> <%= employee_id %></p>
      <% } %>

      <p class="paragraph">This is with regard to your resignation,</p>

      <p class="paragraph">
        Dated
        <%= new Date(resignation_date).toLocaleDateString('en-GB').replace(/\//g, '-') %>
        from the position of <strong><%= designation %></strong> — We would like to inform you that you have been relieved of your duties at the end of business hours of
        <%= new Date(relieving_date).toLocaleDateString('en-GB').replace(/\//g, '-') %>.
      </p>

      <p class="paragraph">
        We enjoyed working with you and thank you for the service rendered from
        <strong><%= new Date(start_date).toLocaleDateString('en-GB').replace(/\//g, '-') %></strong>
        to
        <strong><%= new Date(relieving_date).toLocaleDateString('en-GB').replace(/\//g, '-') %></strong>.
      </p>

      <p class="paragraph">We wish you good luck for future endeavours.</p>

      <p class="sincere-line">Yours sincerely,</p>
      <p class="for-company-line">For Amazon IT Solutions</p>

      <% if (signaturePath) { %>
        <div style="margin-top: 5mm;">
          <img src="<%= signaturePath %>" alt="Authorized Signature" style="width:90px; height:auto; opacity:0.95;" />
        </div>
      <% } %>

      <p class="signature"><%= hrName %></p>
      <p class="paragraph" style="font-weight: bold;"><%= hrDesignation %></p>

      <p class="note">Note: This is a computer-generated document. No Signature is required*</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
